high_descs: Turn around to reach the kitchen sink.
Pick up the wine bottle from the sink.
Turn around and head to the fridge on the left.
Cool the wine bottle in the fridge and take it out.
Turn left to reach the cabinet under the pumpkin.
Put the wine bottle in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled wine bottle in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left and walk, then turn left and walk towards the sink.
Pick up the wine bottle from the sink.
Turn back and walk then turn left towards the fridge.
Put the wine bottle into the last rack of the fridge and pick it up back.
Turn left and walk towards the sink cabinet.
Put the wine bottle inside the sink cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled wine bottle inside the sink cabinet.

high_descs: Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the cabinet on your right
Pick up wine bottle from the cabinet
Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near fridge
Place wine bottle inside the fridge and then take it out
Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the cabinet
Place wine bottle on the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Place wine bottle inside fridge and placing it in cabinet
